= Introduction

This template entry demonstrates the public `setup(...)` API from `lib.typ`.

You can keep chapter content in `sections/` while letting the root file focus on document metadata, front matter, and overall assembly.

For bibliography validation, this starter chapter cites both @wang2010guide and @kopka2004guide so the references page is exercised during compilation.

For reusable formatting helpers, import only what a chapter needs from `../../lib.typ` instead of rebuilding page-level logic manually.
